The Last Holy War! (Part 2) The Triumph of the Power to Dream
Honey the Bride! The Light of Love is Forever

description: THE HEART-STOPPING SEASON FINALE — Everyone’s lives are in danger as Ra’s al Ghul (guest star Matt Nable) puts forth his final plan. Oliver/Al Sah-him (Stephen Amell) must decide if he’s strong enough to take on this new role and what it will mean for everyone on Team Arrow, and his soul.
name: My Name is Oliver Queen

description: Hulk chases Leader back in time to the Jurassic era, but their actions result in present Earth being taken over by dinosaurs. Hulk battles Leader in the past to save all of time.
name: Days of Future Smash: Part 1 - The Dino Era

series.name: Hulk and the Agents of S.M.A.S.H.

description: The Simpsons learn about Grampa's days in the Air Force, and Bart takes up smoking to impress Milhouse's Dutch cousin, Annika.
name: Let's Go Fly A Coot

description: When Beast Boy's head starts to rattle, Robin suggests that he should find a hobby so that his brain will stop shrinking. Beast Boy and his brain agree to take up gardening.
name: Head Fruit

description: Marooned on an alien world, Cuber must rely on his bag of Graybles to survive.
name: Graybles 1000+

description: Liv (Rose McIver) and Clive (Malcolm Goodwin) work together to solve the murder of a morning radio talk show host who specialized in relationship straight talk. Liv becomes filled to the brim with insight after consuming the brains, making Clive extremely uncomfortable when Liv starts getting personal. Meanwhile, Peyton (Aly Michalka) steps in to help Major (Robert Buckley), and Blaine (David Anders) issues a warning. Lastly, Ravi's (Rahul Kohli) unexpected romantic connection has the potential to make things awkward for Liv.
name: Dead Air

description:
Part 2.

Coulson and his team will be forced to make shocking sacrifices that will leave their relationships and their world changed forever
name: S.O.S. Part 2

description: Liv investigates the death of a former sniper while also discovering her new zombie boyfriend Lowell may not be that trust worthy..
name: Patriot Brains

description: The true power of sway comes out and Royalle tries to recruit Walker to his cause. Meanwhile the CHAOTIC CHIC movement makes their move but this turns out to be a grave mistake on Crispin's part.
name: Aha Shake Heartbreak

description: In a episode written by Powers creator Brian Micheal Bendis - Walker and Royalle prepare to kill Walker by breaking into the Powers prison but both seem to have their own endgames.
name: Level 13

description: Wolfe has escaped and can now suck out the powers of any person who has taken sway. The entire powers division is mobilized and Walker has to chose what he really wants. Plus - a ending that will shape the universe for years to come.
name: F#CK the Big Chiller

description: After Bart gets bullied at the school dance, Marge convinces the town to pass anti-bullying legislation. Homer then gets arrested and sent to rehab for bullying Ned Flanders, only to subsequently leave rehab as a hero.
name: Bull-E

description: Beast Boy and Cyborg decide to make a yearbook for the Titans.
name: Yearbook Madness

description: A charismatic stranger in Finn's dream leads Cosmic Owl to shirk his duties.
name: Hoots

description: When a modernized Springfield Elementary has a technical meltdown, Lisa transforms it into a Waldorf school. Meanwhile, Groundskeeper Willie becomes the coach of the mathletes.
name: Mathlete's Feat

description: Lois books a fun couple's vacation in the Bahamas, but much to Peter's surprise, it turns out to be a marriage counseling program instead. Meanwhile, Carter watches the kids at home and becomes frustrated that they're too into their electronics to play games the old-fashioned way. So he tries to fix it himself.
name: Take My Wife

description: Hulk follows Leader back in time to the Viking Era and teams up with young Thor and Loki. The Agents of S.M.A.S.H. fight to stop 'All Father' Leader from taking over the planet.
name: Days of Future Smash: Part 2 - Smashguard

series.name: Hulk and the Agents of S.M.A.S.H.

description: Wells (Tom Cavanagh) presents Barry (Grant Gustin) with a life-changing choice. Dr. Martin Stein (guest star Victor Garber) and Ronnie Raymond (guest star Robbie Amell) return to help the S.T.A.R. Labs team with this final fight.
name: Fast Enough
The Case of the Cola Cult

description:
Proper Japanese Title: 開始

Ryota Skamoto is one of Japan’s leading BTOOOM! players. He soon wakes up to find that it’s no longer just a game.
name: Start

description:
Proper Japanese Title: 血の女子高生

A typical high school girl is first betrayed by her neighbors. After being forced to participate in the game, she is again betrayed by the people who are supposed to be her team.
name: The Bloodstained High School Girl

description:
Proper Japanese Title: サバイバル

While chasing a mystery girl, Ryota runs into Taira Kiyoshi who helps fill in the blanks in his memory.
name: Survival

description:
Proper Japanese Title: 世界ランカー

Kira Kosuke’s true nature emerges while on the island, and he faces off with the best BTOOOM! player in Japan!
name: Best in the World

description:
Proper Japanese Title: 強襲

A pantless corpse floats by Taira and Sakamoto while they are eating lunch. When Sakamoto leaves to investigate he finds gruesome scene and a familiar figure.
name: Attack

description:
Proper Japanese Title: 生贄の夜

In the moment of danger, trust issues start to show between Taira and Sakamoto. Sakamoto wants to save everyone, especially the girl who just tried to kill him.
name: Night of Sacrifice

description:
Proper Japanese Title: 仮想花嫁

Miyamoto, the mercenary, has found Sakamoto and his team. This dangerous player will do anything it takes to win.
name: Virtual Bride

description:
Proper Japanese Title: 白い亡霊

As Sakamoto and Himiko try to rest for the night, Himiko wrestles with the idea of telling Sakamoto her true identity, but before she can do anything she is visited by a "ghost".
name: White Ghost

description:
Proper Japanese Title: 最強プレイヤー

A new player has joined Sakamoto's team, but he carries a dark secret. Before the team could dive deeper into the new players past, a food drop overhead brings many players out of hiding.
name: The Strongest Player

description:
Proper Japanese Title: ハイレベル

It's revealed that they players are connected in multiple ways. Meanwhile, the doctor begins his end game!
name: High Level

description:
Proper Japanese Title: 復活

Now that Ryouta is out of the way, Himiko becomes an easy target.
name: Revival

description:
Proper Japanese Title: 絆

Ryouta doesn't want to fight, but now that Taira is off his rocker and attacking his friends, he is left with little choice.
name: Bonds
Make New Friends but Keep Discord

series.name: My Little Pony: Friendship is Magic

description:
Proper Japanese Title: 骨でした。 (Hone Deshita.)

Staz Charlie Blood is a powerful vampire with a huge love for Japanese anime and games. When a young schoolgirl named Fuyumi wanders into his territory, Staz cannot hide his excitement at meeting a living human from his favorite culture.
name: She's A Skeleton Now!

description:
Proper Japanese Title: ただいまは言わない (Tadaima wa Iwanai)

Staz’s dream of visiting Japan finally comes true when he escorts Fuyumi back to the human world. But Fuyumi, now a ghost, is not too thrilled with Staz disrupting her once peaceful human life.
name: Back Home, But Not Really!

description:
Proper Japanese Title: 持ってんじゃん (Motten jan)

Staz and Fuyumi head out to West Demon World in search of the Book of Human Resurrection, where they are greeted by Wolf, the territory boss in charge of that area.
name: You Had It All Along

description:
Proper Japanese Title: 殿堂魔界へ (Dendō Makai e)

A reluctant Staz visits Demon World Acropolis to seek his older brother, Braz D. Bloods, the author of the Book of Human Resurrection and the only one who can decipher it.
name: To Demon World Acropolis

description:
Proper Japanese Title: 未確認魔人物体 (Mikakunin Majin Buttai)

While being incarcerated in Liz’s Toy Box, Staz receives a visit from his brother Braz, who offers him a deal: in exchange for giving him the knowledge of human resurrection, Staz must destroy a monster.
name: Unidentified Demon Object

description:
Proper Japanese Title: それがダチ (Sore ga Dachi)

Staz arrives in North Demon World where Wolf is engaged in a fierce battle with the Artificial Demon Akim Papradon.
name: That's Friendship

description:
Proper Japanese Title: はじめてのリズ (Hajimete no Rizu)

Braz leaves Liz under the care of Staz and returns to Demon World Acropolis alone, having obtained the sample of Fuyumi’s magic required to resurrect her back into a human.
name: Liz, For the First Time

description:
Proper Japanese Title: ふたりはトレジャー (Futari wa Torejā)

Liz returns to Demon World Acropolis and discovers that the Acropolis Police are after Braz. Meanwhile, Staz finds the man who kidnapped Fuyumi, only to let him escape.
name: Two Is A Treasure

description:
Proper Japanese Title: メガネの罪 (Megane no Tsumi)

The Acropolis Police bring in Braz for questioning before Wolf-Daddy, the king of Demon World Acropolis. Meanwhile, Fuyumi is brought to the subspace world Hydra.
name: Sins of the Eye Glasses

description:
Proper Japanese Title: ダークヒーロー・ライジング (Dāku Hīrō Raijingu)

A man tied to Fuyumi’s past tells Staz about the events that took place at the Yanagi residence 14 years ago. The man then asks how Staz really feels about Fuyumi.
name: The Dark Hero Rises

description:
Proper Japanese Title: 私が…ゾンビに…なったら (Watashi ga...Zonbi ni...Nattara)

When the family cat is accidentally killed, zombie buff Chihiro Furuya secretly tries to bring it back to life. After he overhears Rea Sanka shouting her frustrations down a well, Rea offers to help Chihiro, as they both keep each others' secrets.
name: If I...Became...A Zombie

description:
Proper Japanese Title: 成功…してた (Seikō...shiteta)

Rea continues to assist Chihiro's attempt to reanimate Babu. She reveals her home life, including an unhealthy relationship with her father. The two of them decide to make one last attempt to bring Babu back to life, using a hydrangea blossom.
name: I...Succeeded

description:
Proper Japanese Title: さんか…れあ (Sanka...Rea)

Rea is grounded indefinitely for sneaking out at night, and her father decides to keep her home from school, for good measure. She sneaks out again anyway, and goes looking for Chihiro. Elsewhere, when Babu runs away, Chihiro and Ranko chase after him.
name: Sanka...Rea

description:
Proper Japanese Title: 普通の…女の子… (Futsū no... Onnanoko...)

Aria learns that Rea has run away, and Dan'ichiro vows to get her back. In Chihiro's room, Rea sews up her wound, and the two of them each come to terms with her rebirth as a zombie. Free of her father, Rea reveals to Chihiro what she now wants from him.
name: A Normal... Girl...

description:
Proper Japanese Title: ゾンビって…コトは… (Zonbitte... Koto wa...)

With Rea going through rigor mortis, Chihiro does his best to keep her hidden while attending to household chores. While trying to figure out how to preserve Rea's body, Chihiro makes a startling discovery about his grandpa. Ranko learns more about Rea.
name: Being A Zombie... Means...

description:
Proper Japanese Title: あなたに…出会えたから (Anata ni... Deaeta kara)

Rea's strange behavior leads her to kiss Chihiro in front of Ranko. After Rea slips away, Chihiro learns some valuable information about the undead from his grandpa. Chihiro decides to start keeping a diary of his observations of Rea.
name: Because... I Met You

description:
Proper Japanese Title: おさな…なじみ… (Osana...Najimi...)

Chihiro spends his Sunday helping out with the Saoji family's restaurant. Ranko tells the tale of the first time she met Chihiro. The two young children develop an unusual friendship between themselves as more about Ranko's family is revealed.
name: Childhood... Friend...

description:
Proper Japanese Title: 偽りの…自由… (Itsuwari no... Jiyū)

After Rea agrees to join the Furuya family in a meal, Chihiro becomes more interested in her dietary habits. At Rea's insistence, he takes her to the mall to shop for clothes. Once there, however, Chihiro isn't the only one who pays attention to Rea.
name: Fake...Freedom...
